# subagent-broker.tape — vhs script for the subagent-broker demo GIF.

Output "demos/subagent-broker.gif"

Set Theme "GitHub Dark"
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1180
Set Height 880
Set Padding 24
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0
Set Framerate 24

Hide
Type "clear && bash demos/scenario-subagent-broker.sh"
Enter
Show

Sleep 17s
